What you need to know:  When she announced the Justice (rtd) Aaron Ringera-led Caretaker Committee CS Amina was faced with a myriad of hurdles by some football followers — especially those sympathetic to the cause of the disgraced former FKF boss Nick Mwendwa — who thought that the CS had committed a foul thus deserving a yellow card, if not an outright red card.According to those in this school of thought, Mwendwa was the right man for the job and should have been left to run with his showboating—despite an audit report unearthing missing millions of shillings and other acts of malfeasance on part of the president.